==Suspected offenses==
In addition to numerous burglaries, Colton has allegedly stolen four airplanes by hot-wiring and then crash-landing them. It is believed that his knowledge of flying such light aircraft has been learned by means of reading flight manuals and handbooks. He once went to a house to have a shower and stole ice cream from the freezer, and has also used a computer and stolen credit card in a house to purchase a pair of [[night vision goggles]], among other things, on the Internet.
